8. f4 dxe4 { This trade isn't a good idea. } 9. Nxe4
{ This change in structure makes us very happy because we now control a tremendous amount of space. }
9... Nd7
{ Black is developing a knight, trying to swap a pair of pieces soon after ...Nf6. }
10. Nf3
