11. Bg3 Qxd6 12. O-O
{ With Rad1 coming next, followed by Nd5, or Ne4-d6/c5, we are definitely enjoying a considerable amount of pressure in the center. Black's g7-bishop is also blocked now, which isn't great at all. }
