17. Ne2
{ We are preparing to play c2-c3, which will completely prevent Black's ability to put pressure on the c-file, or down the a1-h8 diagonal. Next, we'll proceed with h2-h3, restricting the opponent's knight, and so on. Crucially, Black cannot win a pawn with ...Nb4. }
