14... bxc5 15. O-O-O
{ Black isn't having any fun here. The structure is symmetrical, but the c8-bishop is very passive and we have an outpost on d6 as well as spatial advantage on the kingside. Next, we'll improve our position with f2-f4, maybe h2-h4-h5, Rh3-g3, and so on. Black is suffering, and we are clearly better! }
