15... Rxa5 16. Qb3 Rxa1 17. Rxa1 Ba8 18. Nc4
{ White's pieces are incredibly active, and there is no way to stop threats like Nb6-d5, Bc4 followed by Ng5, etc. The game is about to be over in a few moves! }
